# Vrinda Store Sales Analysis Dashboard

## Objective

Analyze sales performance across states, platforms, and customer segments.

## Tools Used

* Microsoft Excel

## Key Insights

* Maharashtra contributes the highest share of total sales
* Amazon and Flipkart generate ~57% of total sales
* 92% delivery success rate indicates strong operations

## Skills Demonstrated

* Data Cleaning
* Pivot Tables
* Dashboard Creation
* Business Insights
